We have to use Amazon's SES for sending email - to prevent our email
from being tagged as spam.

1. Set up unstable package rep in apt/sources.list
2. Update exim4
   sudo apt-get install exim4 exim4-base
3. Configure /etc/exim4/exim4.conf as described here:
   http://docs.amazonwebservices.com/ses/latest/DeveloperGuide/SMTP.MTAs.Exim.html
4. May need to hard code ETC_MAILNAME values as appropriate
